title: AWS EC2: Instance Status
agents: aws
catalog: cloud/aws
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the instance and system status.

 To make this check work you have to configure the related
 special agent {Amazon Web Services (AWS)}.

 If both tests (system and instance) have passed the check is {OK} otherwise {CRIT}.

inventory:
 One service is created if all required metrics (StatusCheckFailed_System, StatusCheckFailed_Instance) are given.
